ransaction details. We record and review complaints, may request evidence, and will communicate the outcome where appropriate.</p><?php else: ?><p>We aim to provide an accessible service. If you experience a barrier, contact support and tell us the page, device and assistance needed.</p><?php endif; ?></div></section><?php $this->endSection(); ?>
